{
  "stem": "25912.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- there were notices all over the place, inviting people to report voluntarily for deportation to the east and being promised bread and jam if they went voluntarily.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some people went, especially desperate ones, the ones who were hungry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were great discussions going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a wonderful teacher I had in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I think it was Miss Dorothy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think it was Marienstadt Morganstadt, something of that kind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had-- it was a group that was [NON-ENGLISH], Boden, whose father was killed by the Russians in Katyn Forest.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was Elisa Regirer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was Elizabeth, who was a niece of our teacher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think there were four other-- I can't remember any other names.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And she and her niece and whoever was in the family, I don't remember, they decided to report.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People were saying, if we go voluntarily, then it will be better than if we are rounded up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the number of volunteers dwindled, and the Germans resorted to rounding people up for deportation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At that time, it was said that if you were working for the German war effort, you would not be deported.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I don't know who set up workshops all over the place, including one behind that church, which I mentioned before-- and people were given [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] certificates that they were working for the German war effort.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My mother had one, my grandmother, and my aunt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were all supposed to be attached to the one at this church hall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But of course, I was too young to have one.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
